data.description: LAKEFRONT BEAUTY! Better than Brand New! Loaded with Upgrades.  Ready for immediate Occupancy.  Freshly painted Exterior; New Roof-2022 with transferrable warranty; Brand New Pool Cage 7/2023 with designer expanded panoramic view and No See-um screens; New Marcite Pool & Spa resurfacing 2022 and painted coolcrete deck 2023; Hurricane Impact Resistant Windows and Roll Down Screens-2021 providing 100% Wind Mitigation Certification Insurance discounts. This 3 Bedroom, 2 bath great room, open floor plan features high volume ceilings; tile floors galore; plenty of windows & doors to welcome the outside in. Updated, open, Entertainment style kitchen with cabinets galore, miles of new granite countertops, stainless appliances with gas range and new counter height breakfast bar.  Casual dining area adjoining the kitchen with triple disappearing sliders to the lanai and pool.  Plus, extra bonus space perfect for at-home office or game room for your pool table.  Open Great room with huge wall to mount your super sized flat screen tv.  Extended Master en-suite with french door access to the pool and an extra area to create your own comfy reading nook. Updated Master bath with his and her walk-in closets, new granite countertops, cabinetry, mirrors and fixtures, tiled walk-in shower, linen and private commode.  Updated Utility room with new cabinetry, work counter, washer, dryer and utility sink.  Updated Guest bath with new granite countertops, vanity, sink, mirror and fixtures.  Extra features you will appreciate include:  Space Saver Closets, Plantation Shutters, Garage Storage Cabinet, workbench, ceiling storage rack and utility hangers; Extra Attic insulation and flooring; Upgraded Landscape with Curb-it edging; Newer Pool gas heater and variable speed pump; plus more.  Absolutely nothing to do -- Totally extra special -- just move right in!  Greenbrook Village with low HOA fees offers 2 community adventure parks providing miles of hiking and biking trails, dog parks, volleyball, soccer, playgrounds, sports fields and sidewalks.  Plus, Lakewood Ranch Master Planned Community provides you with every need within minutes from home:  Grocery, Dining, A-Rated Schools, Parks, Healthcare, Day Care, Recreation Parks, Tennis, Golf, Fitness, YMCA, Churches, Premier Sports Park Campus plus much more.
